sentence: Among the underlying components of the Russell 3000 index, we saw noteworthy options trading volume today in Proofpoint Inc (Symbol: PFPT), where a total of 2,958 contracts have traded so far, representing approximately 295,800 underlying shares.
That amounts to about 47.2% of PFPT's average daily trading volume over the past month of 627,085 shares.
Particularly high volume was seen for the $115 strike call option expiring February 15, 2019 , with 590 contracts trading so far today, representing approximately 59,000 underlying shares of PFPT.

That number of contracts represents approximately 313,200 underlying shares, working out to a sizeable 47.1% of GRA's average daily trading volume over the past month, of 665,225 shares.
Especially high volume was seen for the $72.50 strike call option expiring February 15, 2019 , with 2,642 contracts trading so far today, representing approximately 264,200 underlying shares of GRA.
